  "description": "Use this form to extend your existing visa under Tier 1 (Investor) or to switch into it from another immigration category.",
  "details": {
    "body": "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Use this form if you are in the UK on a Tier 1 (Investor) visa and you want to extend your stay or you are in the UK under a different immigration category and you want to switch to Tier 1 (Investor).</p>\n\n<<p>Read the Tier 1 (Investor) guidance notes for further information.</p></div>",
